            "type": "section",
            "text": {
               "type": "mrkdwn",
               "text": "\n>Hey there! Welcome to the JHS Robotics Team #$1! We are proud to have you on our team and we look forward to working with you. If you have any questions, you can contact us at $2. Or if you really need to, talk to one of our team members."
            },
