            "type": "divider"
         },
         {
            "type": "section",
            "text": {
               "type": "mrkdwn",
               "text": "In order for you to become a full member of the team, please register by typing the following command:```/register```"
            }
         },
         {
            "type": "section",
            "text": {
               "type": "mrkdwn",
               "text": "Or if you feel like this isn't the club/team for you. You can leave by talking to *$3* in room *$4* or by executing the command: ```/leave```"
            }
         },
         {
            "type": "context",
            "elements": [
               {
                  "type": "mrkdwn",
                  "text": "*PS:*  $5 is also a great source for answering any questions you have!"
               }
